---
title: Brain Matters
pageable: true
layout: blog
---

- content_for :blog_title do
  Posts from
  - if page_type == 'day'
    = Date.new(year, month, day).strftime('%B %e, %Y')
  - if page_type == 'month'
    = Date.new(year, month, 1).strftime('%B %Y')
  - if page_type == 'year'
    = year

- page_articles.each_with_index do |article, i|
  = partial 'blog_entry', locals: { article: article }
